&lt;p&gt;We are looking to recruit a Registered Nurse for our multidisciplinary Outpatient service which includes clinics in Alwoodley, Yeadon, Wetherby and Ripon Hospital.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We specialise in a number of areas including: Surgery, ENT, Urology, Ophthalmology and Dermatology.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for an enthusiastic nurse, keen to take on training in all these specialties, with the support of our cohesive multi-disciplinary team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You will be able to:-&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;• Demonstrate excellent interpersonal skills&lt;br /&gt;• Aspire to deliver excellent standards of care &lt;br /&gt;• Be able to work collaboratively with all members of the multi-disciplinary team&lt;br /&gt;• Demonstrate a high level of compassion for patients and their relatives&lt;/p&gt;
